Sultan Ana — Privacy Policy (English)
Last updated: July 14, 2026 · Vainsteel Studios

This policy explains how Sultan Ana — Dream Meanings & Daily Horoscope, developed by Vainsteel Studios, handles your data.

In short
None of the personal information you enter leaves your device. It is never sent to us or to any server, and we do not store it. No account or sign-up is required.

Information stored on your device
Your name, birth date, birth time and gender (used for horoscope, rising sign, biorhythm and numerology), your dream texts and journal, and your app preferences are stored only on your device and are used solely to run the app.

Photos (fortune features)
For the coffee, palm and eye reading features, any photo you choose is processed entirely on your device — the app measures general visual properties such as brightness, color and texture locally. Your photo is never uploaded to any server, is not stored by us, and is not kept in memory after the reading. The app performs no face recognition or biometric identification.

Ads
The app shows ads via Google AdMob, which may process your device's Advertising ID to serve and measure ads — the only data collected, handled directly by Google (see the Google Privacy Policy). Purchasing ad removal or the Supporter Pack disables ads entirely.

Purchases
Ad removal (remove_ads) and the Supporter Pack subscription (supporter_pack) are handled through Google Play Billing. We never see or store your payment details; your purchase status is kept on your device only to unlock the relevant features.

Notifications, deletion & children
Local notifications are generated on your device with your permission and collect no data. All app data is deleted when you uninstall the app or clear its data. The app is not directed at children and is intended for users aged 18 and over.

About the content
Sultan Ana is the app's guide character; readings are generated automatically from an in-app symbol database and are not professional advice.

